page.title: 07LIFE STYLE OF A GIRL
page.content: At about 7.00 I get up and wash,dress and have breakfast.I then feed the Guinea Pigs and the Fish and collect my bag.I leave the house at 8.30 and walk the hundred yards to where I catch the bus.At 9.00 we either have assembly or a long registration. First break is from 10:35 to 10:55,lunch is from 12:10 to 1:20 and last break is from 2:40 to 2:50.At 4:00 the bell goes and we all line up to catch the buses.There are about fifteen altogether.When I reach home I get washed and changed and fetch my brother and then usually cook tea.I then read or draw and do any homework,until I go to bed.I go to bed at about 9:30 to 10:00 on week days.
